Instrument(s)/Platform(s): GlucoSure STAR Blood Glucose Monitoring System
Document Summary: FDA 510(k) summary for Contrex Plus Low Control Solution as a quality control material for validating blood glucose monitoring systems
Indications for Use Summary: Validates the performance of GlucoSure STAR & GlucoTRACK Blood Glucose Monitoring Systems using a control solution with a known range of glucose to ensure proper user technique and device function
